duties_responsibilities.duty: Generate and sustain sphere and personal leads to drive real estate transactions.
Provide supportive and encouraging guidance to clients in their real estate endeavors.
Show up for yourself and your clients, and guide your own growth and success as an independent Realtor.
Manage transactions and contracts to ensure a smooth and successful real estate process for clients.
Network and build relationships to expand your client base and increase lead generation.
Stay up-to-date with market trends and property values to provide valuable insights to clients.
